            "description": "\u003Ctable width='815'\u003E\u003Ctbody\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003ETYPE\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd width='591'\u003ECombined Drought Index\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003EDATA PRODUCTS\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd width='591'\u003EIndex Maps\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003ETITLE\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd width='591'\u003ECombined Drought Index (CDI)&nbsp;\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003EABSTRACT\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd width='591'\u003EMaps processed by Philippine Space Agency (PhilSA). The datasets used were GPM rainfall, MODIS NDVI, and MODIS LST. The datasets are processed in Python with machine learning to forecast Combined Drought Index Maps. The maps were processed monthly from December 2023 to April 2024\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003EPURPOSE\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd width='591'\u003EThe Combined Drought Index is a monitoring index to provide insights to the severity, location, timing and duration of drought over a region.\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003ETEMPORAL START AND END DATE\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd width='591'\u003E01/01/2024 - 31/01/2024\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003ESPATIAL REPRESENTATION TYPE\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd width='591'\u003ERaster, GeoTIFF\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003EREGIONS\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd width='591'\u003EPalawan\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003EDATA QUALITY STATEMENT\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd width='591'\u003EA combination of GPM Rainfall, MODIS NDVI, and MODIS LST used machine learning-based forecasting in Python. The Drought Index is displayed at a 500m spatial resolution.\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003ECATEGORY\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd width='591'\u003EEnvironment\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003EKEYWORDS\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd width='591'\u003EDrought, NDVI, LST, MODIS, GPM\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003EEDITION\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd width='591'\u003E1/1/2024\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003Ctr\u003E\u003Ctd width='224'\u003ELICENSE\u003C/td\u003E\u003Ctd\u003EThe use of the datasets provided herewith are covered by End Users License Agreement (EULA)\u003C/td\u003E\u003C/tr\u003E\u003C/tbody\u003E\u003C/table\u003E"
